      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil</strong> a kettle</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong> all the potatoes to roughly equal size (approx. 4cm chunks)<br /><br /><strong>Add</strong> the potatoes and salt (optional) to a pot of boiling water and boil for 15 min or until you can pierce them easily with a fork</p>",
