    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Slice</strong> each pork loin steak in half lengthwise, to form 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">(8)</span> escalopes</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Lay your hand flat over the steaks and carefully saw through with a sharp knife</p>\r\n<p><strong>Coat</strong> one escalope with the seasoned flour, tapping off any excess</p>\r\n<p><strong>Dip</strong> it in the egg and coat well, then roll it in the breadcrumbs and coat evenly</p>\r\n<p><strong>Repeat</strong> with the remaining steaks</p>",
