      "instruction": "<p><strong>Grate</strong> the zest of the lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span><br /><br /><strong>Slice</strong> the spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span> finely, discarding the root end<span class=\"text-danger\">(s)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Dice</strong> the apple finely (approx. 1cm thick), discarding the core</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chop</strong> the celery finely (approx. 1cm thick)</p>",
